goals__remit: The company has been active for eight year. The core activities are related to development of zero energy construction project, providing experts services for REA of EC (evaluation ENG panel of FP-7, Horizon 2020), teaching in fields of circular economy, environmental engineering.
relevant_communication: Providing training on resource efficiency issues. Evaluation of Horizon 2020 projects in different fields: climate change, waste, energy efficient construction, recycling of construction waste, innovative training networks, twinning etc. Elaboration of teaching materials to explain life cycle approach (http://foodweb.ut.ee/s2/111_232_82_Ketsupi_olelusring.pdf)
